## 1-drawings

Working UFO sources.

## master\_ufo

*Do not edit manually, content generated by script*.

UFO masters build by `buildMasters.py` from `1-drawings` and used to build the variable font.

## master\_ttf\_interpolatable

*Do not edit manually, content generated by script*.

TTF masters build by `fontmake` from `master_ufo` and used to build the variable font.
